				</app>
			</div>--><div type="translation"><p n="1"> Success! Homage to the Bhagavant, the Perfect Buddha, who is
					ensconced in the excellent relic [or: element (<hi rend="italic">i.e.</hi>, <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">nirvāṇadhātu</foreign>)]! </p><p n="1-3"> At the Great Shrine, ...
